00:49:23.176 --> 00:49:28.448 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Time to get on her feet—
Try to make ends meet—

00:49:28.448 --> 00:49:35.555 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Never sure what to expect.
Her true friends out there

00:49:35.555 --> 00:49:42.562 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Really show her they care,
So she never needs to fret.

00:50:21.668 --> 00:50:27.340 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
She’ll soar on wings
To rise up high,

00:50:27.340 --> 00:50:33.213 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Like eagles in the sky.
All the roles she plays—

00:50:33.213 --> 00:50:40.287 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So little time each day—
And in her heart, she starts to pray.

00:50:40.287 --> 00:50:49.896 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Aching feet and tired hands—
She tries the very best she can.

00:50:49.896 --> 00:50:58.238 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But there’s strength she can find
In that song that’s always on her mind:

00:50:58.238 --> 00:51:08.482 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
