00:51:53.827 --> 00:51:56.396 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’ve seen many examples of modesty

00:51:56.396 --> 00:51:58.398 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
on the program this month.

00:51:58.932 --> 00:52:01.768 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
First, the McConnell sisters helped us appreciate

00:52:01.768 --> 00:52:03.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that true family happiness

00:52:03.770 --> 00:52:07.741 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
is only possible when we
follow Jehovah’s principles.

00:52:07.741 --> 00:52:10.677 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Modest parents know their limitations

00:52:10.677 --> 00:52:13.446 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and will rely on Jehovah’s guidance.

00:52:14.381 --> 00:52:18.151 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
After the talk,
we saw how a young brother’s modesty

00:52:18.151 --> 00:52:21.254 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
protected him from sinning against Jehovah.

00:52:22.622 --> 00:52:26.326 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Next, we saw examples
of organizational achievements,

00:52:26.326 --> 00:52:29.196 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
all of which require modesty.

00:52:29.196 --> 00:52:33.533 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We saw this not only
in the Faith in Action Museum at Warwick

00:52:33.533 --> 00:52:35.902 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but also with the satellite provision

00:52:35.902 --> 00:52:38.004 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for JW Broadcasting®

00:52:38.004 --> 00:52:40.507 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in sub-Saharan Africa.

00:52:41.141 --> 00:52:43.643 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And we need to be careful not to confuse

00:52:43.643 --> 00:52:47.614 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
our imperfect view of ourselves with modesty.

00:52:47.614 --> 00:52:51.818 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Instead, we should do all we can
to support Jehovah’s work.

00:52:51.818 --> 00:52:55.455 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And as we do,
Jehovah will support us,

00:52:55.455 --> 00:52:58.925 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
as this month’s music video highlighted.

00:52:58.925 --> 00:53:02.495 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And later this month,
you’ll find an exciting report

00:53:02.495 --> 00:53:04.664 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
on Video on Demand.

00:53:04.664 --> 00:53:08.468 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s about the work of the Publishing Committee
of the Governing Body.

00:53:08.468 --> 00:53:11.271 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So tune in again for that.

00:53:11.271 --> 00:53:13.273 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To conclude,

00:53:13.273 --> 00:53:17.777 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
let’s visit our brothers
and sisters in Tasmania, Australia.

00:53:19.246 --> 00:53:23.550 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Tasmania is Australia’s smallest state

00:53:23.550 --> 00:53:27.821 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and is an island located about 240 kilometers,

00:53:27.821 --> 00:53:31.324 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or 150 miles, south of the mainland.

00:53:31.324 --> 00:53:33.760 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Despite its small land mass,

00:53:33.760 --> 00:53:36.796 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
it’s known for its very diverse landscape

00:53:36.796 --> 00:53:39.933 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
featuring beautiful yet rugged mountain,

00:53:39.933 --> 00:53:42.602 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
lake, and coastal landscapes.

00:53:44.004 --> 00:53:47.340 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The central plateau
is a prominent feature of Tasmania,

00:53:47.340 --> 00:53:50.443 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
thanks to its more than 4,000 lakes

00:53:50.443 --> 00:53:52.712 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of glacial origin.

00:53:52.712 --> 00:53:56.750 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This island is home to close to 1,800 publishers

00:53:56.750 --> 00:53:58.752 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in 22 congregations.

00:53:59.753 --> 00:54:02.689 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And this is the Huonville Congregation.

00:54:03.490 --> 00:54:07.360 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They care for Australia’s southernmost territory.

00:54:07.360 --> 00:54:09.930 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Although their territory is vast

00:54:09.930 --> 00:54:13.333 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and many of the publishers
are advanced in years,

00:54:13.333 --> 00:54:17.337 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the congregation is known
to assist neighboring congregations

00:54:17.337 --> 00:54:19.406 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with their territories.

00:54:19.406 --> 00:54:24.077 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In 2016,
the Huonville Congregation

00:54:24.077 --> 00:54:27.647 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
was happy to see
their Kingdom Hall get renovated.

00:54:27.647 --> 00:54:31.952 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And when visiting brothers
come to give a public talk in Huonville,

00:54:31.952 --> 00:54:35.956 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
it’s not unusual that they get
a box of local produce as a gift.

00:54:37.490 --> 00:54:41.127 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Our brothers and sisters
in the Huonville Congregation

00:54:41.127 --> 00:54:44.230 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
send us their warm Christian love,

00:54:44.230 --> 00:54:47.901 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and we love them very much.

00:54:47.901 --> 00:54:51.938 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Until next month,
this is JW Broadcasting

00:54:51.938 --> 00:54:55.942 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
from the World Headquarters
of Jehovah’s Witnesses.

